beer.beer_description:
Crying Heidi is collaboration NEIPA between Willie the boatman, Cryermalt & Yakima Chief hops.
Using Best Malz Heidelberg malt as a base creating a very light malt profile, this New England IPA is light and juicy using fresh hops from Yakima Chief Hops newest harvest creating a beautiful tropical hop profile.
MALT Heidelberg, Oats, Wheat, Chit
HOPS Azacca, Citra, El Dorado
